textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value LINK_ENCAP (Link encap:\S+)
Value HWADDR (HWaddr \S+)
Value INET_ADDR (inet addr:\S+)
Value BCAST (Bcast:\S+)
Value MASK (Mask:\S+)
Value INET6_ADDR (inet6 addr: \S+/\d+ Scope:\S+)
Value UP (UP)
Value BROADCAST (BROADCAST)
Value RUNNING (RUNNING)
Value MULTICAST (MULTICAST)
Value LOOPBACK (LOOPBACK)
Value MTU (MTU:\d+)
Value METRIC (Metric:\d+)
Value RX_PACKETS (RX packets:\d+)
Value RX_ERRORS (errors:\d+)
Value RX_DROPPED (dropped:\d+)
Value RX_OVERRUNS (overruns:\d+)
Value RX_FRAME (frame:\d+)
Value TX_PACKETS (TX packets:\d+)
Value TX_ERRORS (errors:\d+)
Value TX_DROPPED (dropped:\d+)
Value TX_OVERRUNS (overruns:\d+)
Value TX_CARRIER (carrier:\d+)
Value COLLISIONS (collisions:\d+)
Value TXQUEUELEN (txqueuelen:\d+)
Value RX_BYTES (RX bytes:\d+ \(\d+\.\d+ \w+\))
Value TX_BYTES (TX bytes:\d+ \(\d+\.\d+ \w+\))

Start
  ^${INTERFACE}\s+${LINK_ENCAP}\s+${HWADDR}\s*$$
  ^\s+${INET_ADDR}\s+${BCAST}\s+${MASK}\s*$$
  ^\s+${INET6_ADDR}\s*$$
  ^\s+${UP}\s+${BROADCAST}\s+${RUNNING}\s+${MULTICAST}\s+${MTU}\s+${METRIC}\s*$$
  ^\s+${RX_PACKETS}\s+${RX_ERRORS}\s+${RX_DROPPED}\s+${RX_OVERRUNS}\s+${RX_FRAME}\s*$$
  ^\s+${TX_PACKETS}\s+${TX_ERRORS}\s+${TX_DROPPED}\s+${TX_OVERRUNS}\s+${TX_CARRIER}\s*$$
  ^\s+${COLLISIONS}\s+${TXQUEUELEN}\s*$$
  ^\s+${RX_BYTES}\s+${TX_BYTES}\s*$$
  ^\s*$$
  ^${INTERFACE}\s+${LINK_ENCAP}\s*$$
  ^\s+${INET_ADDR}\s+${MASK}\s*$$
  ^\s+${INET6_ADDR}\s*$$
  ^\s+${UP}\s+${LOOPBACK}\s+${RUNNING}\s+${MTU}\s+${METRIC}\s*$$
  ^\s+${RX_PACKETS}\s+${RX_ERRORS}\s+${RX_DROPPED}\s+${RX_OVERRUNS}\s+${RX_FRAME}\s*$$
  ^\s+${TX_PACKETS}\s+${TX_ERRORS}\s+${TX_DROPPED}\s+${TX_OVERRUNS}\s+${TX_CARRIER}\s*$$
  ^\s+${COLLISIONS}\s+${TXQUEUELEN}\s*$$
  ^\s+${RX_BYTES}\s+${TX_BYTES}\s*$$
